@node hist "History."

 It took us 4 days to write it.
 4 weeks to improve it.

 First the program needed 4MB of memory to run.
 Then we started cutting it.

 We had to get rid of Ren animation at the end.
 It needed a double buffer which killed all the memory.

 When the program was finally done, I had to come up with the
 high score idea. It took me all night to figure out the best
 way to do it.

 I have to send thanks to Paul Polak for testing the program.
 I don't know how many times he had to upload it and play with it.

 Since this was our first program, I'm sure that there is still
 lots of things that could be done better.

 For now we are starting to get sick of this program :)
 That's why now you get it :)
@endnode
